          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Temporary price data. Calculated as 90% of purchasers price based on: 94% of the average price (to account for a 6% loss in transformation and transmission) for electricity for industrial consumersin 2005 (excluded taxes). From IEA.</comment>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">For structural reasons of the ecoinvent database the annual import volume is set to zero in this dataset. The import volume is considered directly in the respective high voltage electricity market of the importing geography.</productionVolumeComment>
